<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>If you fancy watching the Uefa Champions League Final with royalty – then here's your chance.</p>

<p>Hotels.com has put the once-in-a-lifetime experience of watching the match with King Eric Cantona up for grabs.</p>

<p>The lucky winner (and a friend) will sit down to watch the game on Sunday, August 23, with the former Manchester United star at the rustic – and luxurious - 'Casa de Cantona' in rural Provence.</p>

