<p>The King himself will be the host for a 'suave summer soiree'.</p>

<p>The agenda includes a pre-match French feast, TV room 'service', an optional dip in the pool at half-time and punditry from Monsieur Cantona, of course.</p>

<p>He'll be right there to discuss game tactics and exchange poetry, too, if the winner so desires.</p>

