<p>Hotels.com said: 'Eric will be handing over keys to the luxury abode in Provence for two nights, as well as hanging around to enjoy the big game build-up and the match itself. That means it's time to start practising your anthem singing, chants and most importantly, your Cantona poetry.'</p>

<p>Cantona, the firm added, has been 'diligently preparing Casa De Cantona for his guests' arrival, making sure his VIPs have the ultimate viewing set-up and the best room in the house'.</p>

<p>You can see these preparations for yourself on this YouTube video.</p>

<p>At the time of writing the teams left in the competition are: RB Leipzig, Atlético Madrid, Paris Saint-Germain, Manchester City, Lyon, Barcelona and Bayern Munich. </p>

<p>The final will be played at Estádio do Sport Lisboa e Benfica in Lisbon, Portugal, but it will be closed to fans.</p>

<p>Cantona claims that Casa De Cantona is the next best thing.</p>

